These environment variables are always set when hooks are executed.

EGGS_USER: person who triggered the event.
EGGS_LINE: The full IRC line.
EGGS_WHEN: When the event happened.
EGGS_WHERE: the channel or user name.

CONCIEGGS_DIR: main concieggs directory.
CONCIEGGS_DB_DIR: writable data storage directory.
CONCIEGGS_IRC_DIR: the ii directory.
CONCIEGGS_NAME: name of the bot.
EGGS_DIR: root EggsML directory.
EGGS_LIB_DIR: location of useful commands.
